# API & Workers Rules

## Stack

FastAPI + Pydantic (API). Celery + Redis (workers). Python type hints required.

## Patterns

- Routers thin; logic in `services/`
- Pydantic schemas mirror `packages/shared-types`
- Celery tasks idempotent — retries must not duplicate DB rows
- Wrap ffmpeg and external AI calls with error handling

## Logging (required fields when available)

`request_id`, `task_id`, `video_id`, `step`, `model`, `duration_ms`, `retry_count`

## AI Output

Parse → validate → normalize → save. Store `asr_model`, prompt version, timestamp. Keep `raw_analysis` for debug.

## Auth

Staging/prod: require `Authorization` header (P6-01). See [security.md](../../docs/operations/security.md).

